episodes.title: Cult or Curse - Dialogs with Ma Anand Sheela | Ep 09
episodes.description:
Ma Anand Sheela, born Sheela Ambalal Patel, gained international attention as the controversial and influential spokesperson for spiritual leader Bhagwan Shree Rajneesh, later Osho. Sheela's leadership at Rajneeshpuram ended in imprisonment for questionable activities related to her commune. After serving her sentence, she moved to Switzerland, now occasionally discussing her past and the Rajneesh movement.
